%% Diagram: Migration TTL lowering timeline — phased TTL changes with safe-cutover window
%% Type: gantt
gantt
    dateFormat  YYYY-MM-DD
    axisFormat  D
    title TTL Lowering Timeline (calendar days)

    section Authoritative
    Old TTL of 3600s active           :done, p1, 2026-04-21, 1d
    Lower TTL to 300s                 :crit, p2, 2026-04-22, 1d
    Drain old TTL                     :active, p3, 2026-04-23, 1d
    Make record change                :crit, p4, 2026-04-24, 1d
    Verify at multiple resolvers      :p5, 2026-04-25, 1d
    Restore TTL to 3600s              :p6, 2026-04-26, 1d

    section Resolver caches
    Old value cached                  :done, r1, 2026-04-21, 2d
    Mixed cache, old draining         :active, r2, 2026-04-23, 1d
    New value visible                 :crit, r3, 2026-04-24, 1d
    Stable on new value               :r4, 2026-04-25, 2d
